:"2020-05-24T01:01:49.000Z","msg":"咁揸車揸到一半罷工比較好"},{"pid":"a264d52a8f34e0470d65f0e597802f451d25e5f6","tid":2031793,"uid":271199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T01:12:25.000Z","msg":"其實罷工係要all行業先有效，一d罷一d唔罷，咁不如唔好罷"},{"pid":"162f6d4903d7176f5611e40306fdd49cd1104101","tid":2031793,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T02:04:54.000Z","msg":"唔記得入滿油停左係路中間公司會追究？"},{"pid":"632876b2506e195fdeef582961861c1c7b4b3276","tid":2031793,"uid":41352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"162f6d4903d7176f5611e40306fdd49cd1104101","tid":2031793,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T02:04:54.000Z","msg":"唔記得入滿油停左係路中間公司會追究？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:00:59.000Z","msg":"啲巴士停哂喺公路會點"},{"pid":"da9807eb39800f23007064976207d127fe74839e","tid":2031793,"uid":133806,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b57c85db4a1a44e36a5614d460f98e6cb33e21cd","tid":2031793,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ff25fcd50d7fc04af2995942748df5abb15b045","tid":2031793,"uid":63979,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"008a056e2d8a62421730e2ebd66ea59c843e5b14","tid":2031793,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T17:01:37.000Z","msg":"交通工具罷咗一半D人咪又係要翻工<br />\n按章工作分分鐘仲有效<br />\n一架列車就塞死晒成條綫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T20:10:09.000Z","msg":"我地要既係擺到明罷工，而唔係咁曖昧似罷唔罷果種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T01:01:49.000Z","msg":"咁揸車揸到一半罷工比較好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:38:18.000Z","msg":"支持車長<strong><ins>安全駕駛</ins></strong><br />\n例如好似英國同日本咁<br />\n1. 對返準站頭上落，等乘客坐好先開車<br />\n2. 永遠行慢線，唔好特登爬頭，普通道路行50，高速公路唔好過70<br />\n3. 如果見到乘客搵八達通／散銀嗰陣，就等佢哋嘟好卡，安頓好先開車<br />\n4. 轉彎時小心啲慢慢過路口，見黃燈就唔好衝，慢慢跣到燈口停，斑馬線見有廢老就停車俾佢哋過<br />\n5. 喺德輔道彌敦道長沙灣道呢啲人多車多嘅路段就唔好過30公里（運輸署都諗住將有啲繁忙路段set巴士行30公里）<br />\n6. 如果遇到問題乘客就勸喻佢哋遵守秩序，唔遵守或者被屌老母唔開心就響台port車<br />\n7. 駛出巴士站嗰陣確認冇車衝出來，揸車要<ins>忍讓</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.td.gov.hk/mini_site/safe_driving_and_health_campaign/image_index/main.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.td.gov.hk%2Fmini_site%2Fsafe_driving_and_health_campaign%2Fimage_index%2Fmain.jpg&h=4bb3c094&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3da1e707d01e261defcf62ed42f0b5439ef91480","tid":2031793,"uid":105976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:42:19.000Z","msg":"&gt; 罷工基金 <br />\n&gt; 聯合埋其他各行各業搞  事半功倍"},{"pid":"1132337d2a3b9a264904a0e30b8164675061ed18","tid":2031793,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:43:28.000Z","msg":"香港你有份, 你想唔想做野先"},{"pid":"4d0c29deac413b57005cee20ea55945a3ec3a994","tid":2031793,"uid":77542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:43:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f0eb7392e7fec62172293a4d016f0cdb86c7e871","tid":2031793,"uid":63979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1132337d2a3b9a264904a0e30b8164675061ed18","tid":2031793,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:43:28.000Z","msg":"香港你有份, 你想唔想做野先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:14:50.000Z","msg":"咁我地會唔會又再一次被condom先？"},{"pid":"4182867d6172d4f99dbeadcc41ce5bf97aa2f9f3","tid":2031793,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d31fafdbb7eb3c3e5232b97f00b6a389945e27c","tid":2031793,"uid":63979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T15:53:38.000Z","msg":"究竟連登仔有幾想我地罷工？<br />\n如果我地罷工會點支援我地？<br />\n<br />\n我地係2019年11月果陣計劃過一d行動，但當時公司要威脅會對工會有行動，我地曾經係連登求助，但個post極速沉底，因為果一次令到我地既會員對工業行動多左好多顧慮！<br />\n<br />\n究竟連登仔想唔想我地做野先？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:16:11.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"ed6b9b73964711efcc1ff47a22467deabb385a4c","tid":2031793,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:16:31.000Z","msg":"唔好亂開頭罷工,冇人會幫到你地"},{"pid":"9b1f627d355d874ea96329eac50b216590b9abc0","tid":2031793,"uid":69503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:18:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ddd6528ba492c2433d64968dc8b4374c11abfc5","tid":2031793,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:33:14.000Z","msg":"罷工無乜用<br />\n賺藍絲錢先有用<br />\n你癱瘓唔到一個月就無謂<br />\n永遠敵強我弱就最好乜都偷偷地做<br />\n你係要結果唔係要好睇<br />\n自hi 完乜都無無謂<br />\n對面都唔會光明正大掉人落樓<br />\n但係手足此終無咗<br />\n做咗乜唔洗同人講<br />\n唔好增加自己危險"},{"pid":"c96cef9bc1618ec24742fbb6d50129740b859de8","tid":2031793,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3da1e707d01e261defcf62ed42f0b5439ef91480","tid":2031793,"uid":105976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:42:19.000Z","msg":"&gt; 罷工基金 <br />\n&gt; 聯合埋其他各行各業搞  事半功倍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主你11月開post 時已經連登已經五毛聖地,<br />\n好多嘢你同其他公會傾下,搵合適嘅時機一齊全港罷工啦！唔洗灰心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4927a95d6844e94967cde02fd392ebebbe7977d2","tid":2031793,"uid":54450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:38:30.000Z","msg":"支持！"},{"pid":"a70aefd6929f54c5f17466050f0decb9fc776060","tid":2031793,"uid":136431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:39:16.000Z","msg":"一定要聯合其他工會<br />\n一呼百應 如果唔係又會虛耗政治能量"},{"pid":"4942827081a6bbfbe1ad7f0f8d3bb43d9be05bfc","tid":2031793,"uid":180931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:4